{"tid":1829033,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"中環遮打花園及遮打道舉行「天下制裁」集會","createTime":"2020-01-18T11:15:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T13:39:14.000Z","uid":216888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ee6e35c317369981fad2d940022e3b105e954288","tid":1829033,"uid":216888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T11:15:54.000Z","msg":"2020-1-18 18:44字體： A A A<br />\n民間集會團隊明天會在中環遮打花園及遮打道舉行「天下制裁」集會，發言人劉頴匡今午召開記者會。他在會上首先帶領其他人高呼「塞爆中環，正式啟動」，其後開始交代集會安排。<br />\n<br />\n劉頴匡預計集會範圍可容納約3至5萬人，呼籲參加者下午2時開始入場，由中環站畢打街出口或香港站，從西面向東面進入參與集會，希望首先「迫爆」遮打花園，再「迫爆」整條遮打道。他稱如果「迫唔爆」，集會如常進行；若場地爆滿，則呼籲市民流水式向東面離開，讓出空間給其他市民由西面參與集會。"},{"pid":"f0e98bd6a60356d98354271ed4a03f42b658570e","tid":1829033,"uid":216888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T11:17:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qW04i3n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqW04i3n.jpg&h=2592b87c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1ff5af737e1a14f6d2482333b3a7e7085eaddf7","tid":1829033,"uid":21887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T13:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278357144749a5af19cf531f683a05230d802115","tid":1829033,"uid":21887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T13:39:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}